<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="worse-adj">worse <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɜːs/    美 /wɜːrs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>更坏 / 差 / 糟的；病情更重的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Your work is bad but mine is much worse. 
你活干得不好，而我干得更糟。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The patient is worse this morning. 
今早病人的病情恶化了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It looks like the weather is changing <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the worse . Shall we stick to our plan?   （2008 辽宁）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>